Synopsis: Generates a random string of characters from a specified character set.
Description: This function generates a random string of characters from a specified character set with the given length.

Examples.Title: EXAMPLE 1
Examples.Code:
Get-RandomCharacters -length 8 -characters 'abcdef123'
Generates a random string of 8 characters from the character set 'abcdef123'.

Examples.Title: EXAMPLE 2
Examples.Code:
Get-RandomCharacters -length 12 -characters 'ABC123!@#'
Generates a random string of 12 characters from the character set 'ABC123!@#'.
